{"tid":1510084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［外國勢力］大家幫手用Twitter 推香港人權法","createTime":"2019-08-27T05:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T09:21:47.000Z","uid":48912,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0390c64345b4e74a701d253dffdf7621c2c5ce9","tid":1510084,"uid":48912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:11:03.000Z","msg":"是旦哥叫大家幫手用Twitter 推香港人權法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ibZv1jN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FibZv1jN.jpg&h=ab2ab39a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/764219590311857/posts/2379586982108435?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F764219590311857%2Fposts%2F2379586982108435%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=c21e8995\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/764219590311857/posts/2379586982108435?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【沒有了白宮聯署點算】<br />\n<br />\n請各位 Twitter User 準備作戰了。既然白宮聯署網唔知幾時先整好，我哋都唔好依賴，每人都幫手在美國國會議員的 Twitter 度留言，請佢哋復會就盡快通過《香港人權及民主法案》吧。<br />\n<br />\nPlease pass the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act in order to ensure that all residents of Hong Kong are afforded freedom from arbitrary or unlawful arrest, detention, or imprisonment.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/speakerpelosi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fspeakerpelosi&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=5db78116\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/speakerpelosi</a> <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/realDonaldTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=9ae761b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/realDonaldTrump</a> <a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/senatemajldr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr&d=9