344&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【現存白宮聯署更新】<br />\n<br />\n明白現在實在太多白宮聯署，好多人會唔記得自己簽咗邊個，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 唔肯定嘅，簽多一次。在我的道德標準下，呢個可以，因為你唔係故意用同一個電郵簽幾次。<br />\n<br />\n2/ 簽咗之後，自己mark返自己簽咗邊個，這是大家的責任。<br />\n<br />\n《未夠數》<br />\n==========<br />\n中國武警冒充香港警察，白宮聯署請求美國國會盡快通過香港人權民主法案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YW8pa8&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=bdf82f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YW8pa8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請求美國取消中國學生簽證<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/30GcBMM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F30GcBMM&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=8764c7d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/30GcBMM</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國派美軍拯救香港巿民<br />\n <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KsmYOQ&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=0cf0a5aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KsmYOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國將中國共產黨定性為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MlpLM3&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=1f2d75ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MlpLM3</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國向北京施壓，停止製造白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Zkc8hX&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=6eac760c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Zkc8hX</a><br />\n<br />\n拯救國泰航空，保障經濟自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZmWgPU&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=f919ea9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZmWgPU</a><br />\n<br />\n要求拒絕前警務處處長曾偉雄到聯合國就任提名<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z0cMkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z0cMkw&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi9B4iDtR